Description:
You leave the elevator and soon you realise the importance of this place: A energy collector is gathering energy from the ancient machine and bumping that power into the workbenches scattered around the area.

The energy collector is buzzing and emits an unsettling noise, as if it were struggling to manage all the power that it is absorbing.

Looking around you realise that the vanguard group passed this way, as there are lot of defeated dwarves laying on the ground.
DescriptionAction: Those workbenches are perfect to assemble the arm to your robot.
